text: Linda Johnsen-Holmeide (born 1 December 1972) is a Norwegian sport wrestler. She won a bronze medal at the 1992 World Wrestling Championships in Villeurbanne, and a bronze medal at the 1993 World Wrestling Championships in Stavern. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian female sport wrestlers Category:World Wrestling Championships medalists
title: Linda Johnsen-Holmeide
